





NBA Basketball

Which NBA player has the best chance to be the scoring champion for the 2017-18 season?

For this project we will analyze player data from across the NBA then employ the appropriate models/approach to create our conclusion. NBA executives for each team can use this information to anticipate spikes or declines in team revenue. If a player leads the league in scoring this has a positive affect on ticket sales, jersey sales and TV primetime exposure.

Our client will be NBA executives

We will analyze data from:

http://stats.nba.com/

https://www.basketball-reference.com/leaders/pts_season.html

